name: Chaos Incarnate (Starter Commander Decks Precon Decklist)

main.name: Kardur, Doomscourge
main.oracle_text:
When Kardur, Doomscourge enters, until your next turn, creatures your opponents control attack each combat if able and attack a player other than you if able.
Whenever an attacking creature dies, each opponent loses 1 life and you gain 1 life.

card.name: Hate Mirage
card.oracle_text: Choose up to two target creatures you don't control. For each of those creatures, create a token that's a copy of that creature. Those tokens gain haste. Exile them at the beginning of the next end step.
card.flavor_text: A trick of the light, though momentary, can still be deadly.

card.name: Rakshasa Debaser
card.oracle_text:
Whenever Rakshasa Debaser attacks, put target creature card from defending player's graveyard onto the battlefield under your control.
Encore {6}{B}{B} ({6}{B}{B}, Exile this card from your graveyard: For each opponent, create a token copy that attacks that opponent this turn if able. They gain haste. Sacrifice them at the beginning of the next end step. Activate only as a sorcery.)

card.name: Reign of the Pit
card.oracle_text: Each player sacrifices a creature. Create an X/X black Demon creature token with flying, where X is the total power of the creatures sacrificed this way.

card.name: Command Tower
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
card.flavor_text:
"Approach my tower on bended knee or depart from it as ash upon the wind."
—Gadwick, the Wizened

card.name: Lightning Greaves
card.oracle_text:
Equipped creature has haste and shroud. (It can't be the target of spells or abilities.)
Equip {0}
card.flavor_text: After lightning struck the cliffs, the ore became iron, the iron became steel, and the steel became greaves. The lightning never left.

card.name: Wild Ricochet
card.oracle_text: You may choose new targets for target instant or sorcery spell. Then copy that spell. You may choose new targets for the copy.
card.flavor_text:
"May your day never match your expectations."
—Scriptus Fleen, flectomancer

card.name: Sign in Blood
card.oracle_text: Target player draws two cards and loses 2 life.
card.flavor_text: Little agonies pave the way to greater power.

card.name: Rakdos Signet
card.flavor_text: Made of bone and boiled in blood, a Rakdos signet is not considered finished until it has been used as a murder weapon.

card.name: Commander's Sphere
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
Sacrifice Commander's Sphere: Draw a card.
card.flavor_text: It harmonizes with the essence of its master.

card.name: Chaos Warp
card.oracle_text: The owner of target permanent shuffles it into their library, then reveals the top card of their library. If it's a permanent card, they put it onto the battlefield.

card.name: Read the Bones
card.oracle_text: Scry 2, then draw two cards. You lose 2 life. (To scry 2, look at the top two cards of your library, then put any number of them on the bottom and the rest on top in any order.)
card.flavor_text: The dead know lessons the living haven't learned.

card.name: Coveted Jewel
card.oracle_text:
When Coveted Jewel enters, draw three cards.
{T}: Add three mana of any one color.
Whenever one or more creatures an opponent controls attack you and aren't blocked, that player draws three cards and gains control of Coveted Jewel. Untap it.

card.name: Sol Ring
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add {C}{C}.
card.flavor_text: Lost to time is the artificer's art of trapping light from a distant star in a ring of purest gold.

card.name: Soul Shatter
card.oracle_text: Each opponent sacrifices a creature or planeswalker with the highest mana value among creatures and planeswalkers they control.
card.flavor_text: The Kargan tribes share legends of the victory their ancestors won over the Akoum Skyclave, and its horrendous cost.

card.name: Ambition's Cost
card.oracle_text: You draw three cards and you lose 3 life.
card.flavor_text:
"Conquering your first world is the hardest, after all. My power grew as I moved from world to world, taking anything that would make the next taking easier."
—Ob Nixilis

card.name: Akoum Refuge
card.oracle_text:
Akoum Refuge enters tapped.
When Akoum Refuge enters, you gain 1 life.
{T}: Add {B} or {R}.

card.name: Abrade
card.oracle_text:
Choose one —
• Abrade deals 3 damage to target creature.
• Destroy target artifact.
card.flavor_text: The Falkenrath progenitor was a vicious falconer, and the line is quick to remind others of its heritage.

card.name: Arcane Signet
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
card.flavor_text: It started as a mere drop of water. The Magic Mirror crystallized it into much more.

card.name: Archfiend of Depravity
card.oracle_text:
Flying
At the beginning of each opponent's end step, that player chooses up to two creatures they control, then sacrifices the rest.
card.flavor_text: "Why would I kill you all? Who then would be left to worship me?"

card.name: Myriad Landscape
card.oracle_text:
Myriad Landscape enters tapped.
{T}: Add {C}.
{2}, {T}, Sacrifice Myriad Landscape: Search your library for up to two basic land cards that share a land type, put them onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.

card.name: Bloodgift Demon
card.oracle_text:
Flying
At the beginning of your upkeep, target player draws a card and loses 1 life.
card.flavor_text: He relishes the devotion of his Skirsdag puppets and their belief that it will earn them immortality.

card.name: Bloodfell Caves
card.oracle_text:
Bloodfell Caves enters tapped.
When Bloodfell Caves enters, you gain 1 life.
{T}: Add {B} or {R}.

card.name: Blasphemous Act
card.oracle_text:
This spell costs {1} less to cast for each creature on the battlefield.
Blasphemous Act deals 13 damage to each creature.
card.flavor_text:
"Holy places are no longer sanctuary from death, and death is no longer sanctuary from anything."
—Thalia, Knight-Cathar

card.name: Burnished Hart
card.oracle_text: {3}, Sacrifice Burnished Hart: Search your library for up to two basic land cards, put them onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
card.flavor_text: Forged by divine hands to wander mortal realms.

card.name: Breath of Malfegor
card.oracle_text: Breath of Malfegor deals 5 damage to each opponent.
card.flavor_text: The blood of the demons quickened as their master rose over the battlefield. The blood of the angels also quickened: here was the chance to finally end the war started millennia ago.

card.name: Brash Taunter
card.oracle_text:
Indestructible
Whenever Brash Taunter is dealt damage, it deals that much damage to target opponent.
{2}{R}, {T}: Brash Taunter fights another target creature.
card.flavor_text: "You hit like a kobold!"

card.name: Terminate
card.oracle_text: Destroy target creature. It can't be regenerated.
card.flavor_text: All suns must set.

card.name: Cinder Barrens
card.oracle_text:
Cinder Barrens enters tapped.
{T}: Add {B} or {R}.
card.flavor_text: A mudflow swallowed the lowlands years ago. All that remains are a bottomless mire and an endless rain of ash.

card.name: Combustible Gearhulk
card.oracle_text:
First strike
When Combustible Gearhulk enters, target opponent may have you draw three cards. If the player doesn't, you mill three cards, then Combustible Gearhulk deals damage to that player equal to the total mana value of those cards.

card.name: Dictate of the Twin Gods
card.oracle_text:
Flash
If a source would deal damage to a permanent or player, it deals double that damage to that permanent or player instead.
card.flavor_text: Iroas and Mogis are as different in appearance as they are in personality.

card.name: Deadly Tempest
card.oracle_text: Destroy all creatures. Each player loses life equal to the number of creatures they controlled that were destroyed this way.
card.flavor_text: When the winds blow out of the abyss, death is the only harvest.

card.name: Dredge the Mire
card.oracle_text: Each opponent chooses a creature card in their graveyard. Put those cards onto the battlefield under your control.
card.flavor_text: Fortunately, the reanimation spell just missed the long-dead colony of dung scorpions.

card.name: Explosion of Riches
card.oracle_text: Draw a card, then each other player may draw a card. Whenever a card is drawn this way, Explosion of Riches deals 5 damage to target opponent chosen at random from among your opponents.
card.flavor_text: "You've got how much gold there?"

card.name: Feed the Swarm
card.oracle_text: Destroy target creature or enchantment an opponent controls. You lose life equal to that permanent's mana value.
card.flavor_text:
"On vile wings and bloody wind, the swarm will rise."
—Skyclave inscription

card.name: Fiery Confluence
card.oracle_text:
Choose three. You may choose the same mode more than once.
• Fiery Confluence deals 1 damage to each creature.
• Fiery Confluence deals 2 damage to each opponent.
• Destroy target artifact.

card.name: Foreboding Ruins
card.oracle_text:
As Foreboding Ruins enters, you may reveal a Swamp or Mountain card from your hand. If you don't, Foreboding Ruins enters tapped.
{T}: Add {B} or {R}.

card.name: Geode Rager
card.oracle_text:
First strike
Landfall — Whenever a land you control enters, goad each creature target player controls. (Until your next turn, those creatures attack each combat if able and attack a player other than you if able.)
card.flavor_text: Its crystalline core refracts light into chaos.

card.name: Guttersnipe
card.oracle_text: Whenever you cast an instant or sorcery spell, Guttersnipe deals 2 damage to each opponent.
card.flavor_text: "I found a new toy. Wanna play?"

card.name: Indulgent Tormentor
card.oracle_text:
Flying
At the beginning of your upkeep, draw a card unless target opponent sacrifices a creature or pays 3 life.
card.flavor_text: The promise of anguish is payment enough for services rendered.

card.name: Kaervek the Merciless
card.oracle_text: Whenever an opponent casts a spell, Kaervek the Merciless deals damage equal to that spell's mana value to any target.
card.flavor_text:
"Rats and jackals feast in his swath, but even they will not walk with him."
—Mangara

card.name: Kazuul, Tyrant of the Cliffs
card.oracle_text: Whenever a creature an opponent controls attacks, if you're the defending player, create a 3/3 red Ogre creature token unless that creature's controller pays {3}.
card.flavor_text: Warning to those who scale the cliffs without paying tribute: it's a long way down.

card.name: Magmatic Force
card.oracle_text: At the beginning of each upkeep, Magmatic Force deals 3 damage to any target.
card.flavor_text: It's the pinnacle of utter destructiveness.

card.name: Mana Geyser
card.oracle_text: Add {R} for each tapped land your opponents control.
card.flavor_text: The Quicksilver Sea hissed and bubbled at the indignity. The Vulshok shaman just smiled.

card.name: Molten Slagheap
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{1}, {T}: Put a storage counter on Molten Slagheap.
{1}, Remove X storage counters from Molten Slagheap: Add X mana in any combination of {B} and/or {R}.

card.name: Nihil Spellbomb
card.oracle_text:
{T}, Sacrifice Nihil Spellbomb: Exile target player's graveyard.
When Nihil Spellbomb is put into a graveyard from the battlefield, you may pay {B}. If you do, draw a card.

card.name: Ob Nixilis Reignited
card.oracle_text:
+1: You draw a card and you lose 1 life.
−3: Destroy target creature.
−8: Target opponent gets an emblem with "Whenever a player draws a card, you lose 2 life."

card.name: Profane Command
card.oracle_text:
Choose two —
• Target player loses X life.
• Return target creature card with mana value X or less from your graveyard to the battlefield.
• Target creature gets -X/-X until end of turn.
• Up to X target creatures gain fear until end of turn. (They can't be blocked except by artifact creatures and/or black creatures.)

card.name: Rakdos Charm
card.oracle_text:
Choose one —
• Exile target player's graveyard.
• Destroy target artifact.
• Each creature deals 1 damage to its controller.
card.flavor_text:
"Let all feel joy in pain."
—Rakdos

card.name: Sangromancer
card.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever a creature an opponent controls dies, you may gain 3 life.
Whenever an opponent discards a card, you may gain 3 life.

card.name: Scythe Specter
card.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever Scythe Specter deals combat damage to a player, each opponent discards a card. Each player who discarded a card with the highest mana value among cards discarded this way loses life equal to that mana value.

card.name: Sepulchral Primordial
card.oracle_text:
Intimidate (This creature can't be blocked except by artifact creatures and/or creatures that share a color with it.)
When Sepulchral Primordial enters, for each opponent, you may put up to one target creature card from that player's graveyard onto the battlefield under your control.

card.name: Smoldering Marsh
card.oracle_text:
({T}: Add {B} or {R}.)
Smoldering Marsh enters tapped unless you control two or more basic lands.
card.flavor_text: The continent of Guul Draz is a geothermal swampland reeking of heat and decay.

card.name: Solemn Simulacrum
card.oracle_text:
When Solemn Simulacrum enters, you may search your library for a basic land card, put that card onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
When Solemn Simulacrum dies, you may draw a card.

card.name: Spiteful Visions
card.oracle_text:
At the beginning of each player's draw step, that player draws an additional card.
Whenever a player draws a card, Spiteful Visions deals 1 damage to that player.
card.flavor_text: Knowledge brings the sting of disillusionment, but the pain teaches perspective.

card.name: Stormfist Crusader
card.oracle_text:
Menace
At the beginning of your upkeep, each player draws a card and loses 1 life.
card.flavor_text:
"As she reached the pinnacle, lightning flashed and her eyes blazed with newfound power."
—Legend of the Gilded Knights

card.name: Stensia Bloodhall
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{3}{B}{R}, {T}: Stensia Bloodhall deals 2 damage to target player or planeswalker.
card.flavor_text: The revelry ends when the supply of fresh ingenues runs dry.

card.name: Sunbird's Invocation
card.oracle_text: Whenever you cast a spell from your hand, reveal the top X cards of your library, where X is that spell's mana value. You may cast a spell with mana value X or less from among cards revealed this way without paying its mana cost. Put the rest on the bottom of your library in a random order.

card.name: Syphon Mind
card.oracle_text: Each other player discards a card. You draw a card for each card discarded this way.
card.flavor_text: When tempers run high, it's easy to lose your head.

card.name: Talisman of Indulgence
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{T}: Add {B} or {R}. Talisman of Indulgence deals 1 damage to you.

card.name: Tectonic Giant
card.oracle_text:
Whenever Tectonic Giant attacks or becomes the target of a spell an opponent controls, choose one —
• Tectonic Giant deals 3 damage to each opponent.
• Exile the top two cards of your library. Choose one of them. Until the end of your next turn, you may play that card.

card.name: Temple of Malice
card.oracle_text:
Temple of Malice enters tapped.
When Temple of Malice enters, scry 1.
{T}: Add {B} or {R}.

card.name: Theater of Horrors
card.oracle_text:
At the beginning of your upkeep, exile the top card of your library.
During your turn, if an opponent lost life this turn, you may play lands and cast spells from among cards exiled with Theater of Horrors.
{3}{R}: Theater of Horrors deals 1 damage to target opponent or planeswalker.

card.name: Thermo-Alchemist
card.oracle_text:
Defender
{T}: Thermo-Alchemist deals 1 damage to each opponent.
Whenever you cast an instant or sorcery spell, untap Thermo-Alchemist.
card.flavor_text: "Madness can't touch a mind ignited by genius."

card.name: Titan Hunter
card.oracle_text:
At the beginning of each player's end step, if no creatures died this turn, Titan Hunter deals 4 damage to that player.
{1}{B}, Sacrifice a creature: You gain 4 life.
card.flavor_text: "Monster or human, my rate's the same."

card.name: Unlicensed Disintegration
card.oracle_text: Destroy target creature. If you control an artifact, Unlicensed Disintegration deals 3 damage to that creature's controller.
card.flavor_text: "I'd stand back if I were you."

card.name: Urborg Volcano
card.oracle_text:
Urborg Volcano enters tapped.
{T}: Add {B} or {R}.
card.flavor_text: Deep in the heart of Urborg lie massive volcanoes whose thick black smoke covers the land with perpetual darkness.

card.name: Vampire Nighthawk
card.oracle_text: Flying, deathtouch, lifelink
card.flavor_text: As they fought the Eldrazi, many vampires learned to live among humans. Others were unable to make the adjustment.

card.name: Wayfarer's Bauble
card.oracle_text: {2}, {T}, Sacrifice Wayfarer's Bauble: Search your library for a basic land card, put that card onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
card.flavor_text: It is the forest beyond the horizon, the mountain waiting to be climbed, the new land across the endless sea.

card.name: Wildfire Devils
card.oracle_text: When Wildfire Devils enters and at the beginning of your upkeep, choose a player at random. That player exiles an instant or sorcery card from their graveyard. Copy that card. You may cast the copy without paying its mana cost.
card.flavor_text: Devils sow grief and harvest glee.

card.name: Worn Powerstone
card.oracle_text:
Worn Powerstone enters tapped.
{T}: Add {C}{C}.
card.flavor_text: Even a fragment of a powerstone contains within it not just energy, but space—vast dimensions trapped in fragile crystal.

card.name: Kardur, Doomscourge
card.oracle_text:
When Kardur, Doomscourge enters, until your next turn, creatures your opponents control attack each combat if able and attack a player other than you if able.
Whenever an attacking creature dies, each opponent loses 1 life and you gain 1 life.
